{"tid":1193314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求咗黃大仙靈簽，問69反送中吉凶（僅供參考）","createTime":"2019-06-09T00:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T03:54:38.000Z","uid":36494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"909c2ac4dec0ac443bbbc82a84f09d90abc0b744","tid":1193314,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:14:33.000Z","msg":"第48簽　中平　古人占驗：卓文君賣酒<br />\n<br />\n繡閣聽琴自起思。改粧夤夜最歡時。<br />\n可憐沽酒臨邛市。才子佳人兩下廚。<br />\n<br />\n仙機：<br />\n孕生女。病求醫。<br />\n行有阻。婚不宜。<br />\n蚕微利。亦有之。<br />\n問謀望。要待時。<br />\n宅無礙。善當為。<br />\n求財者。得微利。<br />\n<br />\n問風水：氣運未當發。<br />\n問遺失：尋之恐未得。<br />\n問自身：自在中有苦。<br />\n問天時：豐熟有虛耗。<br />\n問出行：去之亦無益。<br />\n<br />\n解說及記載：<br />\n(漢朝)。昔卓氏有女名文君。新寡。<br />\n聽司馬相如彈琴。遂起心。<br />\n乘夜奔往相處(談得投機。互傾戀慕)。<br />\n(二人私奔出城)成為夫妻。但家貧。<br />\n兩夫婦在臨邛市。開設酒店。一箇是才子。一箇是佳人。<br />\n兩家都要當爐賣酒。此亦<span style=\"color: red;\">有辛苦之氣象</span>也。<span style=\"color: red;\">司馬相如後大貴</span>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">求得此簽者。凡事要隱忍受苦。先難後易也。<br />\n此簽不得作為吉。亦不得作為凶。祇得平常兩字而已。</span>"},{"pid":"9559a2bd9e0692b701f01d9aa6a1ea96720173b9","tid":1193314,"uid":52230,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:38:32.000Z","msg":"建國又係先難後易 大家唔好放棄<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>槍口一致對外！<br />\n<br />\n不要分化！不要懷疑隊友！<br />\n<br />\n有人被捕立即群擁而上集體救援！<br />\n<br />\n勿比機會警犬單獨拉走同伴！<br />\n<br />\n一切行動必須群體出發！ <br />\n<br />\nStick Together Team! 不要落單！<br />\n<br />\n6.9 GOGOGO!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>唔衝嘅人幫手拖住篤灰狗 <br />\n<br />\n衝嘅巴繼續上前！<br />\n<br />\n齊心！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4529c8c8f82eca226c913138b36095f8c69e3e","tid":1193314,"uid":238973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:40:03.000Z","msg":"習近<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">平</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b575c360bc5512989e0e9a32babbc4f85bcef1","tid":1193314,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:54:38.000Z","msg":"推返上嚟，加油"}]}